description:
Kirishima Tooru, Age 28, Sakuragi Group&rsquo;s wakagashira. &mdash;&mdash;
Happily enjoys doing as he pleases because it&rsquo;s the world of organized crime,
he earned the title, &ldquo;The Demon of the Sakuragi Group.&rdquo;

Then one day,
he ended up in charge of his boss&rsquo;s only daughter!? 
An independent young lady and good-looking yakuza brute&rsquo;s heartwarming (?) comedy!
